# fetchAllDataStoreIdentifiers(_:)

**Type Method**

Fetches an array of identifiers from existing data stores that have identifiers.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor class func fetchAllDataStoreIdentifiers(_ completionHandler: @escaping @MainActor ([UUID]) -> Void)
```

```swift
@MainActor class var allDataStoreIdentifiers: [UUID] { get async }
```

## Parameters

- **completionHandler**: A block to invoke with the fetched list of unique identifiers.
